snippet.title: Team Sonic Racing - Team Gameplay Spotlight
snippet.description:
Take a look at some of the new team mechanics in Team Sonic Racing in this gameplay spotlight!

Team Sonic Racing arrives this winter, and is being developed by SUMO Digital, the team behind both titles in the Sonic & SEGA All-Stars racing series.
